# @custom-repo/infra-env

Env

## Installation

```bash
pnpm add @custom-repo/infra-env
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { Env } from '@custom-repo/infra-env';
```

## Development

```bash
# Build
pnpm exec nx build infra-env

# Test
pnpm exec nx test infra-env

# Lint
pnpm exec nx lint infra-env
```
